-<DIV6 N="B" TYPE="SUBPART">
-<HEAD>Subpart B - Terms and Conditions</HEAD>
-
-
-<DIV8 N="§ 1122.100" TYPE="SECTION">
-<HEAD>§ 1122.100   Purpose of this subpart.</HEAD>
-<P>This subpart provides:
-</P>
-<P>(a) Direction to DoD Components on how to construct the four articles of national policy requirements for inclusion in the general terms and conditions of grants and cooperative agreements.
-</P>
-<P>(b) Standard wording for national policy requirements that are more commonly applicable to DoD Components' grants and cooperative agreements.
-
-
-</P>
-</DIV8>
-
-
