-<P>(ii) Any other procedural instructions related to requests for prior approvals for budget or program revisions (<I>e.g.,</I> to whom requests must be submitted) that are common to the awards using the general terms and conditions. For procedural instructions that will vary from one award to another, it is appropriate to include wording that points to the award-specific terms and conditions as the source of the information.
